    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plunder Maps is about two things: Drawing a treasure map for your buried chests, and plundering chests using treasure maps from other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First you bury your treasure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238450/extras/bad259e2ddf19f737976fefb63555d17.poster.avif?t=1758568433\" width=472 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238450/extras/bad259e2ddf19f737976fefb63555d17.webm?t=1758568433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238450/extras/bad259e2ddf19f737976fefb63555d17.mp4?t=1758568433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then you draw a treasure map</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238450/extras/3b7210bf55b516db8c777a40f2141242.poster.avif?t=1758568433\" width=472 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238450/extras/3b7210bf55b516db8c777a40f2141242.webm?t=1758568433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238450/extras/3b7210bf55b516db8c777a40f2141242.mp4?t=1758568433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And finally you play a map <strong>drawn by another player!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238450/extras/d2d845cb6b36c0fd95d2677ddd0dc129.poster.avif?t=1758568433\" width=472 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238450/extras/d2d845cb6b36c0fd95d2677ddd0dc129.webm?t=1758568433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238450/extras/d2d845cb6b36c0fd95d2677ddd0dc129.mp4?t=1758568433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated islands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Async multiplayer - You upload your maps, other people get to play them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer to bury and plunder treasure with your friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete creative freedom in your treasure map. Go wild!</p></li></ul>",
